---
title: Mexican Beef & Corn Pie with Mashed Potato Topping & Sour Cream
description: Switch up a traditional cottage pie with this Mexican-inspired version. We've added corn to the filling for a little sweetness, Tex-Mex spice blend for oodles of flavour and topped the potato crust with melted cheese.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-beef-corn-pie-520145ff.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/mexican-beef-corn-pie-5d54df337cb1530013137d4f-07e67e12.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/mexican-beef-and-corn-pie-5d54df337cb1530013137d4f
